<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-5225/monolith.png" style="width:100%;" alt="monolith.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:100%;">
<p>在5225/方尖碑事件期间形成的建筑体，拍摄于母体无效化之前。</p>
</div>
